show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/cMCGXV
show.description:
In a world where power and deception are the only rules, an ordinary young woman is forcibly entangled in the ruthless game of politics  caught between identity, betrayal, and conspiracy. A wrongful prison sentence, a shattered bond of motherhood, and an unexpected twist in an engagement… all set the stage for revenge.

Supreme Beauty is a tale woven with drama, secrets, and hidden truths.
